minTrades.description:
minTrades
The min amount of times this trade can be done. Default 3
   
Integer

    
* Default Value is 3
* Minimum allowed is 1
* Maximum allowed is 64

maxTrades.description:

* Minimum allowed is 1
* Maximum allowed is 64
